	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Go into MM during the day, invisible, actually your best bet is to NOT have alot of people with you,(the more people with you, the more you have to worry about keeping all invisible..best to bring 1 or 2 higher lvl';d friendds with)I did that quest with one high level friend. The chick you want is out in the courtyard or something (look on a map before you go) you can waltz right thru there invis...she is protected by 2 gargoyles I believe and there are bloodwolves there but they wont attack you if you leave them alone. When I went we actually pulled her away from the gargoyles and they didnt aggro..but if they do, thats why you have mez. She was easy to kill...if the gargs aggro, mez while your friends pick them off one at a time. Good luck<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
